rows.label: bf10180100_0003
rows.name:
What is this place...?
What's wrong with everyone...?

rows.label: bf10180100_0007
rows.name:
Homura, Hikari... Gramps...
Where are you? Where are you guys?!

rows.label: bf10180100_0010
rows.name: Why Rex-Rex run?

rows.label: bf10180100_0020
rows.name: Tora...

rows.label: bf10180100_0030
rows.name:
Hana... Zeke and Saika...
Don't tell me you're all...

rows.label: bf10180100_0040
rows.name: You having fun, chum?

rows.label: bf10180100_0050
rows.name:
Playing the hero like the kid you are,
stringing us adults along...

rows.label: bf10180100_0060
rows.name: T-that's not-

rows.label: bf10180100_0070
rows.name: Boss is bad friend.

rows.label: bf10180100_0080
rows.name:
Why boss become Driver, when
Tora cannot become Driver?

rows.label: bf10180100_0090
rows.name: Tora try so hard, and for what? It useless!

rows.label: bf10180100_0100
rows.name: Masterpon is right.

rows.label: bf10180100_0110
rows.name:
Rex just have a little luck and
become Driver of Holy Grail?

rows.label: bf10180100_0120
rows.name: Hana never ask to be born as imitation...

rows.label: bf10180100_0130
rows.name: Hana want to be real, too!

rows.label: bf10180100_0140
rows.name: Not fair!

rows.label: bf10180100_0150
rows.name: I bet it felt real good, didn't it?

rows.label: bf10180100_0160
rows.name:
Getting special treatment from everyone,
getting chosen by the Holy Grail...

rows.label: bf10180100_0170
rows.name: Who decided you should have all that power?

rows.label: bf10180100_0180
rows.name:
How about you hand it over
to the Prince right now.

rows.label: bf10180100_0190
rows.name: He deserves it.

rows.label: bf10180100_0200
rows.name:
Stop it already!
I did nothing wrong to any of you!

rows.label: bf10180100_0210
rows.name: So you haven't worked that out, either?

rows.label: bf10180100_0220
rows.name:
In your hurry to get here,
you never stopped to consider...

rows.label: bf10180100_0230
rows.name: all the things you left lying in your wake!
